{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"DataTransferItemList","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransferItemList","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTML_Drag_and_Drop_API\">HTML Drag and Drop API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransferItemList\"><code>DataTransferItemList</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransferItemList/length\"><code>length</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DataTransferItemList/add\"><code>add()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DataTransferItemList/clear\"><code>clear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DataTransferItemList/remove\"><code>remove()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for HTML Drag and Drop API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer\"><code>DataTransfer</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransferItem\"><code>DataTransferItem</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DragEvent\"><code>DragEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><code><strong>DataTransferItemList</strong></code>&nbsp;对象是一组代表被拖动项的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransferItem\"><code>DataTransferItem</code></a> 对象的列表。在拖动操作期间，每个<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DragEvent\"><code>DragEvent</code></a> 都有一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DragEvent/dataTransfer\" title=\"dataTransfer\"><code>dataTransfer</code></a> 属性，该属性是&nbsp;<code>DataTransferItemList</code>.</p>\n\n<p>该接口没有构造函数</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"datatransferitemlist.length\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransferItemList/length\"><code>DataTransferItemList.length</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>&nbsp;<code>无符号长整型</code>&nbsp;：列表中拖动项的数量。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"datatransferitemlist.add_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DataTransferItemList/add\"><code>DataTransferItemList.add()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>向拖动项列表中添加新项&nbsp;(<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a>对象或<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\" title=\"string\"><code>string</code></a>)，该方法返回一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransferItem\"><code>DataTransferItem</code></a> 对象。</dd>\n <dt id=\"datatransferitemlist.remove_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DataTransferItemList/remove\"><code>DataTransferItemList.remove()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>根据索引删除拖动项列表中的对象。</dd>\n <dt id=\"datatransferitemlist.clear_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DataTransferItemList/clear\"><code>DataTransferItemList.clear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>清空拖动项列表。</dd>\n <dt id=\"datatransferitemlist.datatransferitem_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DataTransferItemList\"><code>DataTransferItemList.DataTransferItem()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>取值方法：返回给定下标的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransferItem\"><code>DataTransferItem</code></a>对象。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>每个方法或属性都有其引用页面，每一个引用页对应也有使用示例。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">备注</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/interaction.html#datatransferitemlist\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">DataTransferItemList</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/editing.html#datatransferitemlist\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">DataTransferItemList</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Not included in W3C HTML5 <span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.DataTransferItemList","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransferItemList/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"DataTransferItemList 对象是一组代表被拖动项的DataTransferItem 对象的列表。在拖动操作期间，每个DragEvent 都有一个 dataTransfer 属性，该属性是 DataTransferItemList.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"DataTransferItemList","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"DataTransferItemList","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder